data.description: What more could you ask for in a beautiful, well cared for end unit townhome? Upgrades galore, mountain views and a great location. When you walk into the home you will immediately notice the stained glass panel in the foyer and that this home has it all with a kitchen that everyone dreams of with a ''modern feel'' of classy granite contertops, ''soft close'' cabinets and SS appliances. The bathrooms also boast comfort and style as the vanities, showers and toilets have all been replaced. Southwestern paint colors give the home additional charm on top of all the upgrades (see the upgrades list in documents). As you walk through the home you will notice all windows & window coverings have been updated along with a new Rheem HVAC system in 2015. Don't forget to enjoy the mountain views in the living room and on the back patio. As you walk out onto the patio you will see the area behind the wall is designed for a game of horseshoes or rings for your daytime or evening entertainment with friends. This townhome has it all and won't last long! Schedule your showing appointment today!
